        {
            "title": "英超｜拉舒福特不吃回頭草 傳已決定今夏正式轉會維拉",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"拉舒福特不吃回頭草，傳已決定今夏正式轉會維拉。REUTERS\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/1cb43362ece02d63650caa6b91a1cc89/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250301/_2025030112291719023.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">拉舒福特不吃回頭草，傳已決定今夏正式轉會維拉。REUTERS</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p><p lang=\"zh-TW\" xml:lang=\"zh-TW\">拉舒福特由曼聯借到阿士東維拉後表現脫胎換骨，連同周五英格蘭足總盃<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">16</font>強對卡迪夫城交出<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">1</font>次助攻，加盟維拉以來上陣<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">6</font>次已經累積<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">3</font>次助攻。同時，福仔今仗有<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">6</font>次創造機會，已平了效力曼聯的單場創造機會最多紀錄。福仔非常滿意在維拉的表現和進展，更有傳他已經決定不再返回曼聯，打算今夏借用期滿後正式轉投維拉。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特(右)與新隊友馬高阿辛斯奧(左)擦出火花。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/57aea531fd4138e43b65953dab3fad96/2025-03/2025-02-28T212915Z_1579538791_UP1EL2S1NOQJV_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-AVL-CAR-REPORT_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特(右)與新隊友馬高阿辛斯奧(左)擦出火花。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特(右)與新隊友馬高阿辛斯奧(左)擦出火花。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b7ae9ca516cfc189bf5d742b05ccc98f/2025-03/2025-02-28T212839Z_1965519778_UP1EL2S1NNPJP_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-AVL-CAR-REPORT_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特(右)與新隊友馬高阿辛斯奧(左)擦出火花。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"傳拉舒福特決定今夏正式轉會阿士東維拉。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5dc80eb68b0fdea70785a9e18a9f1959/2025-03/2025-02-28T214140Z_1875920046_UP1EL2S1O9ELD_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-AVL-CAR-REPORT_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        傳拉舒福特決定今夏正式轉會阿士東維拉。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特(圖)加盟阿士東維拉表現脫胎換骨。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/55af2fc90b6e61927ac85392ccd42b45/2025-03/2025-02-28T212956Z_920227299_UP1EL2S1NPUJY_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-AVL-CAR-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特(圖)加盟阿士東維拉表現脫胎換骨。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特(左)獲阿士東維拉領隊艾馬利(中)賞識。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/65eba252dc06bb0dda630da3f89a550f/2025-02/2025-02-09T190130Z_443310395_UP1EL291GUGSR_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-AVL-TOT-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特(左)獲阿士東維拉領隊艾馬利(中)賞識。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"魯賓艾摩廉指拉舒福特離隊是解脫。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1f9faee6daee5bdcc361a0011e33304b/2025-02/11_12.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        魯賓艾摩廉指拉舒福特離隊是解脫。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特今季在曼聯的表現劣評如潮，一直長坐冷板凳。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8f2db4e2eac64f8ab3e0528cd25df7d3/2025-02/2024-12-30T210919Z_1229887038_UP1EKCU1MRI5L_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-MUN-NEW-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特今季在曼聯的表現劣評如潮，一直長坐冷板凳。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"魯賓艾摩廉指拉舒福特離隊是解脫。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b56ab09c2342c546f9dfadfa7ddc4457/2025-02/10_10.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        魯賓艾摩廉指拉舒福特離隊是解脫。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特未獲曼聯新帥魯賓艾摩廉重用。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0afa8519b3c8f20c56a2c9406cd8b664/2025-02/Britain_Soccer_Europa_League_95751--a1b9e.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特未獲曼聯新帥魯賓艾摩廉重用。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"傳拉舒福特決定不重返曼聯。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1f49f12fb77d42dcad882f85905b90d1/2025-01/17_1.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        傳拉舒福特決定不重返曼聯。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2 lang=\"zh-TW\" xml:lang=\"zh-TW\">拉舒福特轉投維拉重生</h2>\n<p lang=\"zh-TW\" xml:lang=\"zh-TW\">拉舒福特在曼聯易帥之後，一直不受新帥魯賓艾摩廉重用，更與對方鬧意見，最後於今年一月被外借維拉。福仔轉投維拉之後如重獲新生，前一仗的英超大戰主場對車路士助攻梅開二度，開啟在新東家的入球、助攻戶口之後，今場足總盃他又助攻予一同在冬季加盟的隊友馬高阿辛斯奧為維拉打開紀錄，各賽事<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">2</font>次正選<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">4</font>次後備上陣已累積交出<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">3</font>次助攻，助攻次數已經追平他上半季為曼聯上陣<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">23</font>次的<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">3</font>次。\n\n</p><p lang=\"zh-TW\" xml:lang=\"zh-TW\">這名英格蘭國腳今仗為維拉<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">6</font>次創造機會，已平了效歷曼聯<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">426</font>仗以來的單場創造機會最多紀錄，而他在<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">2</font>月<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">9</font>日之後於各賽事已經累積<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">13</font>次創造機會，是同期英超球員中最多。有傳正面對前鋒入球荒的曼聯，看到拉舒福特在維拉重拾勇態，考慮在今年夏天前者與維拉借用期滿後重召其歸隊。\n\n</p><h2 lang=\"zh-TW\" xml:lang=\"zh-TW\">福仔決定不會重返曼聯</h2>\n<p lang=\"zh-TW\" xml:lang=\"zh-TW\">據英國《太陽報》報道，拉舒福特很滿意在維拉的表現，並認為維拉領隊艾馬利是最能協助他重拾昔日勇態，爭取重返英格蘭國家隊的最佳人選，故他已經決定不會再返回曼聯效力，打算在借用期滿後正式轉投維拉。亦有報導指拉舒福特向身邊朋友透露，希望在艾馬利的協助之下，可以獲得英格蘭主帥杜曹的賞識，有機會隨英軍出戰<font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">2026</font>年美國、加拿大、墨西哥會辦的世界盃。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2055648/即時-體育-英超-拉舒福特不吃回頭草-傳已決定今夏正式轉會維拉",
